# üß≠ **Which Option Should You Use?**

| Scenario                         | Best Monitoring Option                                |
| -------------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------- |
| M365 Copilot usage analytics     | Microsoft Admin Center (built-in reports)             |
| Copilot Studio agents            | **Application Insights** + Copilot Studio dashboard   |
| Azure-based copilots             | **Azure Copilot Observability Agent** + Azure Monitor |
| Multi-agent or pro-code LLM apps | Microsoft Observability for AI + Application Insights |
| Governance across organization   | **Copilot Studio Monitor (Power BI)**                 |

